  "text": [
    "There is a",
    "distance where",
    "magnets pull,",
    "we feel, having",
    "held them",
    "back. Likewise",
    "there is a",
    "distance where",
    "words attract.",
    "Set one out",
    "like a bait goat",
    "and wait and",
    "seven others",
    "will approach.",
    "But watch out:",
    "roving packs can",
    "pull your word",
    "away. You",
    "find your stake",
    "yanked and some",
    "rough bunch",
    "to thank."
  ],
  "title": "Bait Goat",
  "year": ""
}